cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "AIForge — The Definitive Index of AI, Machine Learning, Deep Learning, LLM, and Data Science Resources"
message: "If you use AIForge, please cite it using these metadata."
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Castro
    given-names: Felipe
repository-code: "https://github.com/FELIPEACASTRO/AIForge"
url: "https://felipeacastro.github.io/AIForge/"
abstract: >-
  AIForge is a comprehensive, curated index of the Artificial Intelligence,
  Machine Learning, Deep Learning, Large Language Model (LLM), and Data Science
  ecosystem. It spans foundational theory, state-of-the-art models, datasets,
  MLOps and production tooling, industry verticals, Kaggle winning solutions,
  the HuggingFace ecosystem, and research/preprint platforms — organized into a
  clean, duplicate-free, English snake_case taxonomy of five pillars plus a
  Frontier AI 2026 innovation radar.
keywords:
  - artificial intelligence
  - machine learning
  - deep learning
  - large language models
  - LLM
  - generative AI
  - data science
  - MLOps
  - datasets
  - awesome list
  - curated resources
  - computer vision
  - natural language processing
  - reinforcement learning
  - Kaggle
  - HuggingFace
